OL,3,C'Failed even in death': Mother speaks
OL,4,Cout after loss of Afghan veteran son
OL,6,FThe mother of a former soldier who is
OL,7,Fthought to have taken his own life
OL,8,Fafter struggling for years with mental
OL,9,Fhealth issues has told ITV News that
OL,10,Fveterans are still failing to get the
OL,11,Fsupport they need and deserve.
OL,13,FWarning: This report contains
OL,14,Fdistressing details.
OL,16,FWords by Paul Tyson, ITV News Senior
OL,17,FNews Editor
