OL,6,FIn the days before he died, he
OL,7,Fappeared to set his affairs in order.
OL,9,FDawn told ITV News: "In my heart of
OL,10,Fhearts, I think it's suicide. He'd
OL,11,Fcontacted all his friends, all his
OL,12,Fsquaddie friends, all his school
OL,13,Ffriends, even contacted his ex-wife...
OL,14,Farranging to meet up, putting things
OL,15,Fin place, saying things like: 'if
OL,16,Fanything happens to me, look after my
OL,17,FMum.'"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
