OL,6,FRobert had tried to take his own life
OL,7,Fbefore. In the aftermath, Dawn set up
OL,8,Fa charity called Stepway to help
OL,9,Fveterans with housing, family and
OL,10,Fmental health problems. Under her
OL,11,Fleadership, the charity was a success,
OL,12,Fattracting solid funding and running
OL,13,Fveteran hubs across the Midlands.
