OL,4,Cout after loss of Afghan veteran son
OL,6,F"I see it day in-day out, and we have
OL,7,Fsaved so many lives and put families
OL,8,Ftogether, but I still couldn't save my
OL,9,Fown son. And if I've got all the
OL,10,Fcontacts and I mean all the ones at
OL,11,Fthe top and I still couldn't make a
OL,12,Fdifference for my son, what hope has
OL,13,Fany other family got?" she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
