OL,3,C'Failed even in death': Mother speaks
OL,4,Cout after loss of Afghan veteran son
OL,6,FRobert had been ill for some time when
OL,7,FDawn arranged a referral to Combat
OL,8,FStress, a charity treating Post
OL,9,FTraumatic Stress Disorder (PTSD) in
OL,10,Fmilitary veterans. There was a six-
OL,11,Fmonth wait for an appointment. She
OL,12,Ftried Operation Courage, the NHS
OL,13,Fmental health scheme for veterans -
OL,14,Fagain, a lengthy wait.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
