OL,3,C'Failed even in death': Mother speaks
OL,4,Cout after loss of Afghan veteran son
OL,6,F"Robert got to the end of his tether
OL,7,Fbecause he'd been to housing, he'd
OL,8,Fbeen to the DWP (Department for Work
OL,9,Fand Pensions), he'd been to mental
OL,10,Fhealth services and there was always a
OL,11,Fbarrier, always a hurdle to jump, it
OL,12,Fwas either a long waiting list or 'you
OL,13,Fare not entitled' or 'you're not a
OL,14,Fpriority,' that's what we kept
OL,15,Fhearing, 'you're not a priority'," she
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
