OL,3,C'Failed even in death': Mother speaks
OL,4,Cout after loss of Afghan veteran son
OL,6,FThe system, she believes, needs
OL,7,Ffundamental change. In theory, the
OL,8,FArmed Forces Covenant assures veterans
OL,9,Fof priority access to government
OL,10,Fservices, but the reality, Dawn says,
OL,11,Fis different.
OL,13,F"It's great on paper, brilliant, we're
OL,14,Fgoing to get priority in housing, in
OL,15,Fhealth, in education, but in reality,
OL,16,Fno, because the system is broken and
OL,17,Fthey can't deliver it, so it's false
OL,18,Fpromises, it's false promises all the
OL,19,Fway through."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
