OL,3,C'Failed even in death': Mother speaks
OL,4,Cout after loss of Afghan veteran son
OL,6,FDawn believes the lack of housing and
OL,7,Fthe lack of timely access to
OL,8,Fhealthcare may have contributed to
OL,9,FRobert's death. And she believes there
OL,10,Fwas something else, too.
OL,12,F"Because we had such a close
OL,13,Frelationship, he didn't want to burden
OL,14,Fme with things, but eventually he
OL,15,Factually broke down, and I mean
OL,16,Fproperly broke down on the floor
OL,17,Fcrying, and he started telling me what
OL,18,Fhe was experiencing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
