OL,6,F"There were lots and lots, but there
OL,7,Fwere things that didn't fit in with
OL,8,FPTSD. He had severe headaches, and he
OL,9,Fgot them so bad that he used to hold
OL,10,Fhis head and say, 'Just make it stop,
OL,11,Fjust make it stop,' and I thought he
OL,12,Fwas on about images, flashbacks, and
OL,13,Fhe wasn't.
OL,15,F"He was in physical pain. And he used
OL,16,Fto say to me, 'You're not listening,
OL,17,Fnobody's listening to me, it's not
OL,18,Fmental, it's physical.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
