OL,6,F"It's only after the event that I
OL,7,Ffound out about traumatic brain injury
OL,8,Fand everything fits in: the fatigue,
OL,9,Fthe mood swings, the change in
OL,10,Fpersonality, it's just blatantly
OL,11,Fobvious now."
