OL,6,FRepeated exposure to blast
OL,7,Foverpressure from heavy weapons or
OL,8,Fexplosives can overwhelm the brain's
OL,9,Fability to heal itself and lead to a
OL,10,Fcomplex constellation of life-changing
OL,11,Fneurological symptoms. There is a well-
OL,12,Fresearched connection between brain
OL,13,Finjury and a higher risk of suicide.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
