OL,6,FRobert's job as an artilleryman in
OL,7,FAfghanistan, firing 105mm light guns,
OL,8,Fmay have exposed him to harmful
OL,9,Foverpressure. The condition is
OL,10,Fheterogeneous, so it affects different
OL,11,Fpeople differently, and symptoms may
OL,12,Fnot appear until long after the
OL,13,Fexposure to blast.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
