OL,3,C'Failed even in death': Mother speaks
OL,4,Cout after loss of Afghan veteran son
OL,6,FBecause some of the effects of TBI
OL,7,Foverlap with symptoms of PTSD, it is
OL,8,Fhard to diagnose, even for mental
OL,9,Fhealth professionals. After death,
OL,10,Fdiagnosis is impossible unless the
OL,11,Fbrain is preserved in time for a
OL,12,Fneuropathological autopsy to be
OL,13,Fperformed.
OL,15,FUnable to see her son for three days
OL,16,Fafter his death, Dawn feels she was
OL,17,Frobbed of the chance to request such a
OL,18,Fprocedure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
