OL,3,C'Failed even in death': Mother speaks
OL,4,Cout after loss of Afghan veteran son
OL,6,FIn her Facebook post shortly after his
OL,7,Fdeath, she wrote: "My son died in the
OL,8,Fearly hours of Saturday morning. We
OL,9,Fcannot see him until Tuesday because
OL,10,Fof the Bank Holiday. Do you know how
OL,11,Fcruel that feels? To know that your
OL,12,Fchild is lying there and you cannot
OL,13,Feven hold his hand, cannot even see
OL,14,Fhis face..."
OL,16,FWe may never know what changed Rob
OL,17,Ffrom the bright, energetic, loving
OL,18,Ffamily man who joined the army to the
OL,19,Ftroubled soul that he became, but Dawn
OL,20,Fhas pledged to fight for answers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
