OL,3,C'Failed even in death': Mother speaks
OL,4,Cout after loss of Afghan veteran son
OL,6,F"He may not have died over in
OL,7,FAfghanistan, but he died for his
OL,8,Fcountry, the country that failed him
OL,9,Fand so many others, and it needs to
OL,10,Fstop, and it needs to stop now. The
OL,11,Fcommunity, society needs to stand,
OL,12,Fmake a stand, all stand together, and
OL,13,Factually look at the proper villain.
OL,14,FAnd that's the government."
OL,16,FA MOD spokesperson said: "Our deepest
OL,17,Fcondolences go out to Robert's loved
OL,18,Fones, and our thoughts and sympathies
OL,19,Fare with them. We ask that their
OL,20,Fprivacy is respected at this difficult
OL,21,Ftime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
